<p rend="chapter">Uṇṇālomikanātha vandanā</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Uṇṇālodhikanāthassa <pb ed="M" n="0.0071" />,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Uṇṇāya bhamukantare;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Vajirāviya sobhanti,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Nikkhanti yo supaṇḍarā.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Vajiragghanakāyassa <pb ed="M" n="0.0072" />,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Nāthassa dehato subhā;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Vajireyyā niccharanti;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Vijjūva gagaṇantare.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Rinindamandahāsena,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Dāṭhāya niccharā pabhā;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Vipphūrisā disāsabbā,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Vajirāyanti paṇḍarā.</p>
